# Phase 4: Streamlit UI — Upload + Preview

Tạo giao diện Streamlit cho pipeline phân tích khảo sát. Phase 4 tập trung vào 2 tính năng chính: Upload file và Show preview.

## Proposed Changes

### UI Layer

#### [NEW] [app.py](file:///d:/Projects/HT_Analysis_Smart/app.py)
Entry point chính cho Streamlit. Cấu hình page, sidebar navigation, session state management.
- Sidebar: navigation giữa các trang (Upload, Preview, Analysis, Results)
- Session state: lưu [SurveyData](file:///d:/Projects/HT_Analysis_Smart/models/data_schema.py#138-227) xuyên suốt workflow
- Page config: title, icon, layout wide

#### [NEW] [ui/pages/upload_page.py](file:///d:/Projects/HT_Analysis_Smart/ui/pages/upload_page.py)
Trang Upload file:
- `st.file_uploader` cho CSV, XLSX, XLS
- Show file info (tên, size, type) sau khi upload
- Auto-run: load → validate → preprocess → quality report
- Hiển thị processing log realtime (progress bar + status messages)
- Show kết quả tổng quan sau khi load xong (shape, encoding, column types, quality score)

#### [NEW] [ui/pages/preview_page.py](file:///d:/Projects/HT_Analysis_Smart/ui/pages/preview_page.py)
Trang Preview dữ liệu:
- **Data table**: `st.dataframe` với full dataset (paginated), search/filter
- **Column info table**: type detected, missing%, scale info
- **Quality report summary**: dataset score, grade, warnings
- **Missing data overview**: bar chart tỉ lệ missing theo cột
- **Data type distribution**: pie chart phân bổ column types

#### [NEW] [ui/data_loader_ui.py](file:///d:/Projects/HT_Analysis_Smart/ui/data_loader_ui.py)
Helper để load `UploadedFile` thành [SurveyData](file:///d:/Projects/HT_Analysis_Smart/models/data_schema.py#138-227):
- `load_uploaded_file(uploaded_file)` → save to temp → call [load_file()](file:///d:/Projects/HT_Analysis_Smart/services/data_loader.py#16-111) → cleanup
- Handles encoding, format detection giống [data_loader.py](file:///d:/Projects/HT_Analysis_Smart/services/data_loader.py)

#### [NEW] [ui/styles.py](file:///d:/Projects/HT_Analysis_Smart/ui/styles.py)
Custom CSS cho Streamlit:
- Color scheme (dark/light), typography
- Card components, metric cards
- Quality score badge styling

